WEBVTT

00:00:00.079 --> 00:00:03.541
As my dear friend,
Dr. Wendy Troxel often says,

00:00:03.583 --> 00:00:05.877
“Sleep is the new sex.”

00:00:05.918 --> 00:00:07.086
And she's right.

00:00:07.086 --> 00:00:11.215
A good night's sleep
will do many things for the vibrancy,

00:00:11.257 --> 00:00:15.053
the intimacy, even the vitality
of your relationship.

00:00:15.636 --> 00:00:18.097
[Sleeping With Science]

00:00:20.183 --> 00:00:23.519
First, when couples
are not getting enough sleep,

00:00:23.561 --> 00:00:26.064
they have more conflicts the next day.

00:00:26.105 --> 00:00:30.318
And furthermore, they don't resolve
those conflicts nearly as well,